metadata.name: Status .tagged_with when given one tag returns the expected statuses

sql_query.sql: SELECT "statuses"."id" FROM "statuses" INNER JOIN "statuses_tags" ON "statuses_tags"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses_tags"."tag_id" = $1 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC
